[normal]worked with economists and other experts on more than six national energy studies and have carried out heat sector and CHP due diligence
[normal],
[normal] acted for EBRD. carrying out due diligence for heat sector work and CHP and are thus familiar with a number of different models for analysing CHP and their defects.  
