[normal]90C flow for supplies on the coldest days
[normal] using 
[normal]dual fuel gas/oil fired eng
[normal]ine CHP installed to back up the 10GW of wind forecast for 2050.
[normal]  The temperatures reflect current Danish practice and the heating system for the city of Odense where coal fired CHP is decarbonising domestic 
[normal]sector buildings
[normal] with domestic gas boilers by co
[normal]nnecting them to district heat.
