[normal]This is a very informative way you have presented the calculation of the efficiency of CHP and insulation.
[normal]It also explains why the building insulation factories
[normal] in e.g. Denmark do not like DH and CHP
[normal]It illustrates that there is a competition between the various methods to provide good indoor comfort.
[normal]It also illustrates why strong commercial interests in the electricity, gas and building material sector in gener
[normal]al are against DH and CHP.
[normal]The consumers and their democratic elected representative are among the few who have interest in DH and CHP
